<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="87" type="colouration">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Colouration.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Body black and shiny, except for the following: mandible (reddish brown apically), labrum, scape, pedicel, flagellomeres I-IV (remainder reddish brown to dark brown), tegula, fore and mid femur extensively (remainder ivory to yellowish), hindleg (basal one third to half of tibia ivory, remainder dark brown) fulvous; palpi and pronotal lobe ivory; forewing veins dark brown; setae on mandible and margin of clypeus golden.</paragraph>
